&lt;h1&gt;Bank Housekeeper&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;How would you like to work for one of the top 20 acute Trusts in the country named as best place to work?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a trust that is growing and developing partnerships with other trusts. We need special people to join us who are motivated to live the Sash values and deliver to our patients compassion, safety, quality dignity and respect demonstrating a one team approach. In return you will be rewarded with a range of benefits including opportunities for personal development and a contributory pension scheme. You need to have excellent customer care skills and a flexible attitude. In recent audits and assessments we have scored highly for cleanliness which is paramount for the well-being and safety of our patients and is the result of the hard work and dedication of our teams. If you have the motivation, skills and experience and would like to be part of a successful organisation please apply.&lt;/p&gt;
